data.title: [1508521049] Spaghetti with Chilli, Sardines & Oregano - Gordon Ramsay
data.description:

Gordon prepares toasted breadcrumbs, finely diced chilli, oregano and garlic, and combines it perfectly with tinned sardines to make a super healthy meal packed with protein. Sardines are an incredibly versatile and nutritious ingredient that adds a real unique flavour to this easy-to-prepare dish.

data.title: [1508521049] Flatbreads with Fennel & Feta - Gordon Ramsay
data.description:
Flatbreads are a traditionally middle-eastern treat and are deliciously versatile, and available from most supermarkets. Here Gordon transforms them by adding thinly sliced fresh fennel, with toasted aromatic fennel seeds and tangy feta cheese, finishing the dish with a sticky and sweet pomegranate molasses. A must-try.

Stuffing the white fish with fennel, dill, capers and lemon, then steaming it in a splash of white wine to create a seriously tasty fusion.
